            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Deep Sleep Hook</h1>
<ul>
<li>Rehide System HUD after sleep / monitor changes / lid changes</li>
<li>Fixed side grow in/out animation that would sometimes get stuck at half</li>
<li>Fixed an issue that prevented internal monitor brightness retrieval after an external monitor was connected</li>
<li>Fixed an issue that was preventing the huds from being shown when changing to a full screen application</li>
</ul>]]></description>
